  ('generalpolice-f3743df6-moex-00021', 'generalpolice-f3743df6', 'generalpolice-f3743df6-moex-114-bb28a373', 'sub-generalpolice-f3743df6-04', NULL, 'essay', '甲獨資設立 A商號，承作乙及所營補習班之影印機出租及維護業務，由
